1
00:00:35,348 --> 00:00:39,000
马达加斯加

2
00:01:17,777 --> 00:01:18,766
吓你一跳!
Surprise!

3
00:01:22,515 --> 00:01:26,281
艾利克斯, 别在我做白日梦来捣乱!
Alex. Do not interrupt me when I'm daydreaming.

4
00:01:26,352 --> 00:01:28,616
斑马在家, 闲人免进
When a zebra's in the zone, leave him alone.

5
00:01:28,688 --> 00:01:31,589
别这样, 马蒂. 我只是想来祝你生日快乐的
Come on, Marty. Just wanted to wish you a happy birthday.

6
00:01:31,657 --> 00:01:33,784
嘿,伙计,谢谢
Hey, man, thanks.

7
00:01:35,495 --> 00:01:38,760
嘿,我牙里塞了点东西
Hey, I got something stuck in my teeth.

8
00:01:38,831 --> 00:01:41,629
快受不了了. 帮个忙,行吗?
It's driving me crazy. Can you help me? Please?

9
00:01:41,701 --> 00:01:44,033
你来对地方了, 我的朋友
You came to the right place, my friend.

10
00:01:44,103 --> 00:01:47,163
马蒂医生,口腔外科学博士,正巧在家
Dr. Marty, D.D.S., is in the house.

11
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:52,268
如果可以的话, 请跳到我消过毒的检查台上来
Please hop on top of my sterilized examination table, if you may.

12
00:01:53,913 --> 00:01:56,541
- 什么也没有呀 - 在左边
- I don't see anything. - It's on the left.

13
00:01:56,616 --> 00:01:57,844
噢, 对不起
Oh, sorry.

14
00:01:57,917 --> 00:02:00,477
好的,嘴里有东西时别讲话
Okay, just don't talk with your mouth full.

15
00:02:01,654 --> 00:02:05,090
找见了,这个鬼东西在这干什么?
Right here. What the heck is this doing in there?

16
00:02:05,158 --> 00:02:06,591
生日快乐!
Happy birthday!

17
00:02:06,659 --> 00:02:09,059
啊,嘿,谢谢啦,伙计
Aw, hey, thanks, man.

18
00:02:09,128 --> 00:02:12,256
你把这个藏在牙后面了. 没错
You put it in behind the tooth. You all right.

19
00:02:12,331 --> 00:02:15,391
这些东西还没有上市呢 来,仔细瞧一下
These aren't even on the shelf yet. Here. Check it out.

20
00:02:15,468 --> 00:02:20,098
- 看这个. 哦! 看呀 - 瞧,下雪了
- Look at that. Ooh! Look at that. - Look at that. It's snowing.

21
00:02:20,173 --> 00:02:22,664
十岁了,是吧？整整十年了
Ten years old, huh? A decade.

22
00:02:22,742 --> 00:02:25,040
两位数字. 大数字啊1-0
Double digits. The big 1-0.

23
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,840
你不喜欢吗？
You don't like it?

24
00:02:28,915 --> 00:02:31,179
-不,不,非常好的礼物 -你讨厌它
- No, no, it's great. - You hate it.

25
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:35,016
我真应该送你艾利克斯的闹钟 那可是个值钱的东西
I should've gotten you the Alex alarm clock. That's the big seller.

26
00:02:35,087 --> 00:02:38,022
不,不,不 这礼物很好,真的
No, no, no. The present's great, really.

27
00:02:38,491 --> 00:02:40,789
只是觉得一年来了又去了
It's just that another year's come and gone

28
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:42,919
而我仍就做着一成不变的事请
and I'm still doing the same old thing.

29
00:02:42,995 --> 00:02:47,830
“从这出发,小跑到那,吃点草, 然后又回到这里”
"Stand over here. Trot over there. Eat some grass. Walk back over here."

30
00:02:47,900 --> 00:02:50,664
- 我知道你的问题了 - 也许我应该去学校读读法律
- I see your problem. - Maybe I should go to law school.

31
00:02:50,736 --> 00:02:53,432
你只需要打破那些令人厌烦的常规就行了
You just need to break out of that boring routine.

32
00:02:53,506 --> 00:02:55,406
-怎么做？ -旧的那套全丢掉
- How? - Throw out the old act.

33
00:02:55,474 --> 00:02:58,773
谁知道你要怎么做 看着编吧
Who knows what you'll do. Make it up as you go along.

34
00:02:58,845 --> 00:03:01,507
即兴表演,编些台词,在空中, 砰,砰,砰
Ad lib. Improvise. On the fly. Boom, boom, boom.

35
00:03:01,581 --> 00:03:03,845
- 真的可以？ - 要来点新鲜的
- Really? - You know, make it fresh.

36
00:03:03,916 --> 00:03:06,316
新鲜点,是吗？好 我会来
Fresh, huh? Okay. I could do fresh.

37
00:03:06,385 --> 00:03:07,443
对我很奏效
Works for me.

38
00:03:12,358 --> 00:03:14,724
有人来了,马蒂 我喜欢人类
Here come the people, Marty. I love the people.

39
00:03:14,794 --> 00:03:16,523
太开心了该人们高兴的时候了
It's fun people fun time!

40
00:03:16,596 --> 00:03:20,396
我们走,格洛丽亚 快出来. 我们的演出开始了!
Let's go, Gloria! Up and at 'em. We're open!

41
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,458
今天星期几？
What day is it?

42
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:24,935
星期五,实习日
It's Friday. Field trip day.

43
00:03:25,004 --> 00:03:28,269
对,实习日 快起床,走...
Yes, it's field trip day. Let's get up and go...

44
00:03:28,441 --> 00:03:30,068
十分钟后见
...in ten more minutes.

45
00:03:31,944 --> 00:03:33,036
赶快！
Come on!

46
00:03:33,112 --> 00:03:36,013
麦尔曼,麦尔曼,麦尔曼！ 麦尔曼,麦尔曼,麦尔曼！
Melman, Melman, Melman! Melman, Melman, Melman!

47
00:03:36,082 --> 00:03:40,348
快起床！太阳都照屁股了！又是纽约市的一个精彩的早晨
Wake up! Rise and shine! It's another fabulous morning in the Big Apple.

48
00:03:40,419 --> 00:03:41,750
咱们出发吧
Let's go.

49
00:03:41,821 --> 00:03:44,813
-我可不去了. 我要请病假 -什么？
- Not for me. I'm calling in sick. - What?

50
00:03:44,891 --> 00:03:48,884
我在肩上又发现了一块晒伤的红斑. 就在这.吓你一跳！
I found another brown spot on my shoulder. Right here. See?

51
00:03:48,961 --> 00:03:50,986
就在这,看到没？
Right there. You see?

52
00:03:51,063 --> 00:03:54,191
麦尔曼,你知道吗 那都是你想象出来的,不是吗？
Melman, you know it's all in your head. Hm?

53
00:03:54,267 --> 00:03:56,098
咱们走！赶快！
Let's go! Come on!

54
00:04:08,514 --> 00:04:11,972
费尔！快起来,你这只让人恶心的猴子
Phil! Wake up, you filthy monkey.

55
00:04:15,521 --> 00:04:17,512
哦,我要变的和以前不一样
Oh, I'm going to be fresh.

56
00:04:17,590 --> 00:04:21,390
从头开始. 要有新鲜感！新鲜的味道
Straight out the ground. Tasty fresh! Freshalicious.

57
00:04:23,529 --> 00:04:24,723
全新的感觉
Ziploc fresh.

58
00:04:24,797 --> 00:04:27,459
女士们先生们,所有的小朋友们,大家好
Ladies and gentlemen, children of all ages,

59
00:04:27,533 --> 00:04:29,865
中央公园动物园现隆重介绍：
the Central Park Zoo proudly presents:

60
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:31,767
快让我们看那头狮子.它是谁？
Show them the cat. Who's the cat?

61
00:04:31,837 --> 00:04:34,135
纽约市之王
The king of New York City.

62
00:04:34,206 --> 00:04:36,731
雄狮艾利克斯
Alex the lion.

63
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:39,007
表演时间到
It's showtime.

64
00:04:43,616 --> 00:04:45,607
（狮子的咆哮声）
Roar!

65
00:04:55,628 --> 00:04:59,394
都到这边来,朋友们 精彩表演马上开始
Gather around, people. Big show about to start.

66
00:04:59,465 --> 00:05:03,196
瞧这只斑马 喜欢做秀. 完全正确
Check out the zebra taking care of biz. That's right.

67
00:05:37,003 --> 00:05:39,198
孩子们,招手微笑
Just smile and wave, boys.

68
00:05:39,271 --> 00:05:41,136
招手微笑
Smile and wave.

69
00:05:41,207 --> 00:05:43,402
克沃斯基,进度汇报
Kowalski, progress report.

70
00:05:43,909 --> 00:05:46,139
我们已经挖到下水主管道外500英尺的地方了
We're 500 feet from the main sewer line.

71
00:05:46,212 --> 00:05:49,204
-坏消息呢？ -我们折坏了最后一支铲子
- And the bad news? - We've broken our last shovel.

72
00:05:49,281 --> 00:05:50,612
好的
Right.

73
00:05:51,217 --> 00:05:54,243
瑞可,你现在去稍微巡视一下 我们需要铲子
Rico, you're on litter patrol. We need shovels.

74
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:58,823
然后再多找些冰糕棍回来 我们可不愿再冒险出现一次塌方事件
And find more Popsicle sticks. We don't want to risk another cave-in.

75
00:05:58,891 --> 00:06:00,153
我呢,斯基泊？
And me, skipper?

76
00:06:00,226 --> 00:06:03,286
我要你装出一副憨态可拘的样子,普莱韦特
I want you to look cute and cuddly, private.

77
00:06:03,362 --> 00:06:05,728
今天我们要好好表演一番
Today we're going to blow this dump.

78
00:06:05,798 --> 00:06:08,460
过来,来这 快来,企鹅
Come here. Come here. Come on, penguin.

79
00:06:12,571 --> 00:06:15,369
是的,在动物星球是看不到这样的表演的
Yeah! You don't see that on Animal Planet.

80
00:06:16,042 --> 00:06:17,168
哈哈
Ha-ha.

81
00:06:17,243 --> 00:06:21,179
好了,演出到此结束, 谢谢光临
Well, show's over, folks. Thanks for coming.

82
00:06:21,247 --> 00:06:23,579
我希望你们感觉这很新鲜
I hope you thought it was fresh.

83
00:06:23,649 --> 00:06:25,173
我整周都会在这里
I'll be here all week.

84
00:06:25,251 --> 00:06:27,845
其实,我会一辈子待在这里
In fact, I'll be here for my whole life.

85
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,252
一年的三百六十五天
Three hundred and sixty-five days a year,

86
00:06:30,389 --> 00:06:34,325
包括圣诞节,光明节和万圣节
including Christmas, Hanukkah, Halloween, Kwanzaa.

87
00:06:34,393 --> 00:06:37,920
请不要忘记给你的宠物做节扎术
Please don't forget to never spay or neuter your pets.

88
00:06:38,631 --> 00:06:41,930
还有给出租车司机小费,因为他没钱花了
And tip your cabbie, because he's broke.

89
00:06:48,407 --> 00:06:51,774
嘿,你,四足动物 说英语吗？
You, quadruped. Sprechen sie Englisch?

90
00:06:51,844 --> 00:06:53,436
我会说
I sprechen.

91
00:06:53,512 --> 00:06:56,675
- 这是哪个洲？ - 曼哈顿区
- What continent is this? - Manhattan.

92
00:06:56,749 --> 00:06:59,684
该死的！我们还在纽约
Hoover Dam! We're still in New York.

93
00:06:59,752 --> 00:07:01,982
艾伯特,跳！跳！快跳
Abort. Dive! Dive! Dive.

94
00:07:02,054 --> 00:07:04,318
嘿,你们穿着礼服.等一下
Hey. You in the tux. Wait a minute.

95
00:07:04,890 --> 00:07:06,824
你们在干什么？
What are you guys doing?

96
00:07:06,892 --> 00:07:08,723
我们在往南极挖洞
We're digging to Antarctica.

97
00:07:09,628 --> 00:07:10,959
南哪个极？
Ant-who-tica?

98
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:14,622
你能保守秘密吗,我的斑纹朋友？
Can you keep a secret, my monochromatic friend?

99
00:07:17,803 --> 00:07:22,001
你以前有见过企鹅在纽约市闲逛的吗？
Do you ever see any penguins running free around New York City?

100
00:07:22,074 --> 00:07:27,137
当然没有.我们不属于这里 这样是违背自然的
Of course not. We don't belong here. It's just not natural.

101
00:07:27,213 --> 00:07:30,512
就象是酒后疯狂的阴谋
This is all some kind of whacked-out conspiracy.

102
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:34,610
我们要到广袤无垠的南极洲去
We're going to the wide-open spaces of Antarctica.

103
00:07:34,687 --> 00:07:36,120
到野外去
To the wild.

104
00:07:37,790 --> 00:07:41,590
野外？ 你们真能去到那里吗？
The wild? You could actually go there?

105
00:07:41,660 --> 00:07:42,991
听起来不错
That sounds great.

106
00:07:44,797 --> 00:07:48,756
嘿,等等,这个地方在哪儿？ 告诉我在哪里？
Hey, hold up. Where is this place? Tell me where it is.

107
00:07:49,602 --> 00:07:52,400
你什么也没看到
You didn't see anything.

108
00:07:52,471 --> 00:07:53,495
对吗？
Right?

109
00:07:53,572 --> 00:07:55,267
不,看到了,先生
Yes, sir.

110
00:07:55,341 --> 00:07:57,002
对不起,是的,什么也没看到,先生
I'm sorry. No, sir.

111
00:07:58,811 --> 00:08:01,575
这是他今天的最后一场演出
For his final appearance of the day,

112
00:08:01,747 --> 00:08:04,739
纽约市之王
the king of New York City.

113
00:08:04,917 --> 00:08:06,475
雄师艾利克司
Alex the lion.

114
00:08:06,685 --> 00:08:08,346
（狮吼声）
Roar!

115
00:08:12,091 --> 00:08:14,082
谢谢.非常感谢
Thank you. Thank you very much.

116
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:17,789
你们很棒,非常配合 也请给自己一些掌声吧
You guys are great. You're a great crowd. Give yourselves a hand.

117
00:08:17,863 --> 00:08:20,161
谢谢.噢.谢谢
Thank you. Oh. Thank you.

118
00:08:20,232 --> 00:08:21,961
哦,好的,谢谢
Oh! Well. Thank you.

119
00:08:22,501 --> 00:08:24,366
噢,你们太友好了.真是太友好了
Oh, that's too kind. Too kind.

120
00:08:27,039 --> 00:08:28,165
哎呀,内裤！
Underpants!

121
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:31,368
祝大伙安全到家.嘿！别忘了查看我的网站
Everybody get home safe. Hey! Check out my Web site.

122
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:34,035
艾力克司24小时视频 看着我入睡
Twenty-four hour Alex Cam. Watch me sleep.

123
00:08:42,388 --> 00:08:44,379
这就是生活
This is the life.

124
00:08:44,857 --> 00:08:46,586
那就是红斑
That's the spot.

125
00:08:46,659 --> 00:08:48,490
啊！我的生活"如此美好"
Oh! I'm in heaven.

126
00:08:58,370 --> 00:09:01,066
-噢,今天是马蒂的生日 -快打开它
- Ooh, it's Marty's birthday. - Just rip it open.

127
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:04,303
-是什么东西呀？ -快点,打开.你得到是什么礼物？
- What is it? - Come on. Open it up. What you got?

128
00:09:04,376 --> 00:09:05,673
一支体温计
A thermometer.

129
00:09:05,744 --> 00:09:09,612
谢谢,麦尔曼,我很喜欢
Thanks. I love it, Melman. I love it.

130
00:09:10,583 --> 00:09:15,179
我想告诉你点私人的事情 这是我第一支肛温计
I wanted to give you something personal. That was my first rectal thermometer.

131
00:09:15,254 --> 00:09:17,347
-天那... -我会想念那个坏孩子的
- Mother... - I'll miss that bad boy.

132
00:09:17,423 --> 00:09:19,118
快拿蛋糕来,麦尔曼,快
Get the cake. Melman, come on.

133
00:09:22,828 --> 00:09:24,693
生日快乐
Happy birthday to you

134
00:09:24,763 --> 00:09:26,697
你生活在动物园里
You live in a zoo

135
00:09:26,765 --> 00:09:29,097
看起来像只猴子
You look like a monkey

136
00:09:29,168 --> 00:09:32,001
而且闻起来也像
And you smell like one too

137
00:09:33,839 --> 00:09:35,204
我说
I say.

138
00:09:36,875 --> 00:09:39,810
啊,现在,你们真让我丢脸
Aw, well, now, you guys are just embarrassing me.

139
00:09:39,878 --> 00:09:41,209
还有你们自己
And yourselves.

140
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:43,680
你在说什么？我们可是练了整整一周啦
What? We worked on that all week.

141
00:09:43,749 --> 00:09:46,547
算了吧 让我们来许个愿,小蛋糕
Let's go. Let's make a wish, babycakes.

142
00:09:52,224 --> 00:09:55,125
-你许的什么愿？ -不. 不能告诉你
- What'd you wish for? - Nope. Can't tell you that.

143
00:09:55,194 --> 00:09:56,354
快点,说吧
Come on. Tell.

144
00:09:56,428 --> 00:09:58,760
不行的,我要是说了就会倒霉的
No siree. I'm telling you, it's bad luck.

145
00:09:58,831 --> 00:10:01,197
你们想倒霉吗 那我就说了
You want some bad luck, I'll blab it out.

146
00:10:01,267 --> 00:10:04,100
不过要是你想平安无事的话, 我一定不会说的
But if you want to be safe, I'll keep my mouth shut.

147
00:10:04,169 --> 00:10:06,729
告诉我们吧 没什么大不了的
Would you just tell us? What could happen?

148
00:10:06,805 --> 00:10:08,067
好吧
Okay.

149
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:12,440
我希望能到野外去！
I wished I could go to the wild!

150
00:10:12,511 --> 00:10:13,739
野外？！
The wild?!

151
00:10:17,549 --> 00:10:19,141
我告诉过你要倒霉的
I told you it was bad luck.

152
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:22,851
野外？你疯了吗？
The wild? Are you nuts?

153
00:10:22,921 --> 00:10:26,015
这是我听到的最糟的想法
That is the worst idea I've ever heard.

154
00:10:28,327 --> 00:10:29,817
那里不卫生的
It's unsanitary.

155
00:10:29,895 --> 00:10:32,989
企鹅们要去那里 为什么我不可以？
The penguins are going. So why can't I?

156
00:10:33,065 --> 00:10:34,589
那些企鹅都是神经病
The penguins are psychotic.

157
00:10:34,667 --> 00:10:38,068
别这样. 想象一下回到大自然的感觉
Come on. Just imagine going back to nature.

158
00:10:38,137 --> 00:10:42,130
回到你出生的地方 清洁的空气,广阔的空间
Back to your roots. Clean air, wide-open spaces!

159
00:10:42,207 --> 00:10:44,675
我听说康乃狄格洲地方特宽敞
I hear there's wide-open spaces in Connecticut.

160
00:10:44,743 --> 00:10:48,110
- 康乃狄格洲？ - 那你得去大中央车站做车
- Connecticut? - You got to go over to Grand Central.

161
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:51,445
然后搭乘北上的火车... 往北走？
Then you got to take the Metro-North train... north?

162
00:10:51,517 --> 00:10:55,749
