马蒂,伙计,听着
Marty. Buddy. Listen.

192
00:13:09,621 --> 00:13:13,717
每个人都有觉得其它地方的草更绿的时候
Everybody has days when they think the grass might be greener somewhere else.

193
00:13:13,792 --> 00:13:14,918
艾利克司
Alex.

194
00:13:15,994 --> 00:13:17,256
看看我
Look at me.

195
00:13:17,329 --> 00:13:20,321
