I like that. I like a little fat on my steak.

245
00:16:23,949 --> 00:16:28,249
美味多汁的牛排 你是难得的美味佳肴
My sweet, juicy steak. You are a rare delicacy.

246
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:31,050
艾利克司.艾利克司.艾利克斯
Alex. Alex. Alex!

247
00:16:31,123 --> 00:16:32,420
怎么了?出什么事了?
What? What?

248
00:16:32,491 --> 00:16:33,617
