I got up to pee and looked over at Marty's pen, which I usually don't do.

253
00:16:45,003 --> 00:16:46,937
我不知道为什么,可就是看了,我发现...
I don't know why, but I did. And...

254
00:16:47,005 --> 00:16:48,495
你发现什么了?到底发生了什么事?
What? What's going on?

255
00:16:48,573 --> 00:16:50,370
我发现马蒂,他走了
It's Marty. He's gone.

256
00:16:50,442 --> 00:16:53,104
走了!你什么意思?
Gone! What do you mean, "gone"?

257
00:16:53,178 --> 00:16:55,840
看来他早有打算!
How long has he been working on this?

258
00:16:55,914 --> 00:16:57,176
马蒂!
Marty!

259
00:16:57,249 --> 00:16:58,614
马蒂!
Marty!

260
00:16:58,684 --> 00:17:00,413
