你应该一直退回到西大街42号
What you got to do is go straight back down West 42nd.

301
00:19:42,347 --> 00:19:44,542
就在你左手边范德比尔特楼后
It's on your left after Vanderbilt.

302
00:19:44,616 --> 00:19:47,881
要是你到了克莱斯勒大楼, 那就是走过头了
If you hit the Chrysler Building, you've gone too far.

303
00:19:47,953 --> 00:19:49,477
谢谢你,长官
Thanks a lot, officer.

304
00:19:51,223 --> 00:19:53,691
嘿,等绿灯亮了再走
Hey! Wait for the light.

305
00:19:54,759 --> 00:19:55,783
怪物
Freak.

306
00:19:55,861 --> 00:19:58,591
- 你刚才说“斑马”？ - 对呀,一匹斑马
- Did you say "zebra"? - That's right. A zebra.

307
00:19:58,663 --> 00:20:00,096
就在我前面
Right in front of me.

308
00:20:00,165 --> 00:20:01,689
