我是说,也许我们也很怕他
I mean, maybe we should be scared too.

798
00:50:38,234 --> 00:50:41,294
要是艾利克斯先生比马岛B更厉害怎么办?
What if Mr. Alex is even worse than the fossa?

799
00:50:42,738 --> 00:50:46,003
跟你说吧,我一看见那个家伙就全身发抖
I tell you, that dude just gives me the heebiedabajeebies.

800
00:50:46,075 --> 00:50:48,566
莫里斯, 你没有举手发言
Maurice, you did not raise your hand.

801
00:50:48,644 --> 00:50:52,375
所以, 对你的评价将会用 历史上最邪恶的字眼
Therefore, your heinous comment will be stricken from the record.

802
00:50:54,083 --> 00:50:56,847
还有别的什么人也对此感到害怕吗?
Does anyone else have the heebie-jeebies?

803
00:50:56,919 --> 00:50:59,387
没有? 好的, 那你就住嘴吧
No? Good. So shut up.

804
00:50:59,889 --> 00:51:02,687
等纽约巨人们醒来后
When the New York giants wake up,

805
00:51:02,758 --> 00:51:08,424
我们一定要让他们感觉像在天堂里一样
we will make sure that they wake up in paradise.

806
00:51:09,799 --> 00:51:12,097
好了,现在,谁想来点饼干?
Now, who would like a cookie?

807
00:51:36,725 --> 00:51:41,594
嗨, 艾利克斯. 麦尔曼和格洛丽亚 在那边开心呢
Yo, Al. Melman and Gloria are over there having a good time.

808
00:51:41,664 --> 00:51:44,224
那边还可以容下一个人
There's room on the fun side for one more.

809
00:51:44,300 --> 00:51:45,927
不, 谢了
No, thanks.

810
00:51:46,001 --> 00:51:50,165
看, 我一直在想 也许,如果你给这个地方一个机会话
Look, I've been thinking. Maybe if you gave this place a chance,

811
00:51:50,239 --> 00:51:53,231
我不确定 但也许它会另你开心的
I don't know, you might even enjoy yourself.

812
00:51:53,309 --> 00:51:56,767
马蒂, 我累了.我饿了
Marty, I'm tired. I'm hungry.

813
00:51:56,846 --> 00:51:58,746
我只想回家去
I just want to go home.

814
00:51:59,915 --> 00:52:03,908
你能不能给它个机会? 考虑一下
Could you just give it a chance? Think about it.

815
00:52:04,820 --> 00:52:07,721
那里要是缺了你就不算是快乐区了
It really isn't the fun side without you.

816
00:52:23,539 --> 00:52:25,166
我知道. 然后...
I know. And then...

817
00:52:28,143 --> 00:52:30,236
-是他 -谁呀?
- It's him. - Who is it?

818
00:52:30,746 --> 00:52:34,045
送比萨饼的 你以为会是谁?
It's the pizza man. Who the heck do you think it is?

819
00:52:34,383 --> 00:52:36,749
是的? 我能帮你什么吗?
Yes? Can I help you?

820
00:52:37,453 --> 00:52:38,977
我能来快乐区吗?
Can I come to the fun side?

821
00:52:41,657 --> 00:52:42,715
您再说一遍?
Beg your pardon?

822
00:52:43,492 --> 00:52:45,722
你知道, 我是个混蛋
You know, I've been kind of a jerk.

823
00:52:47,663 --> 00:52:52,396
但我一直在想你说的话, 我很抱歉
But I've been thinking about what you said, and I'm sorry.

824
00:52:59,675 --> 00:53:03,338
欢迎来到Casa del野生世界 放松一下
Welcome to Casa del Wild. Take a load off.

825
00:53:03,412 --> 00:53:05,380
嘿,嘿, 蹭蹭脚
Hey, hey, wipe your feet.

826
00:53:10,452 --> 00:53:14,548
- 艾利克斯! -我家就是你家
- Alex! - Mi casa is su casa.

827
00:53:21,463 --> 00:53:22,953
布置的不错呀
Very impressive.

828
00:53:23,032 --> 00:53:26,092
嘿,来杯酒吧. 从房上取得
Hey, have a drink. It's on the house.

829
00:53:27,870 --> 00:53:29,132
这是海水
This is seawater.

830
00:53:30,239 --> 00:53:34,039
哦,别咽了. 这只是暂时的 等管道修好了就行了
Oh, you don't swallow it. It's just temporary till the plumbing's done.

831
00:53:34,109 --> 00:53:36,043
嘿, 你看起来很饿
Hey, y'all look hungry.

832
00:53:36,779 --> 00:53:39,805
吃点大自然的馈赠如何?
How would you like some of nature's goodness?

833
00:53:40,916 --> 00:53:42,577
你有吃的?
You have food?

834
00:53:42,651 --> 00:53:45,586
快乐区的特产来了
The Fun Side Special, coming up.

835
00:53:46,288 --> 00:53:48,313
海带串
Seaweed on a stick.

836
00:53:48,891 --> 00:53:49,880
海带?
Seaweed?

837
00:53:50,326 --> 00:53:53,386
穿在棍上 尝一下你才知道它的鲜美
On a stick. Don't love it till you try it.

838
00:54:01,236 --> 00:54:02,794
简直不可相信
That's unbelievable.

839
00:54:04,273 --> 00:54:06,332
-味道真不错 -好,谢谢
- So good. - Well, thanks.

840
00:54:06,408 --> 00:54:09,275
正和口味,对吗?
It does kind of hit the spot, doesn't it?

841
00:54:10,279 --> 00:54:13,510
也许加点柠檬会更好的
Well, maybe it could use a little lemon.

842
00:54:17,486 --> 00:54:21,786
不,这就很好. 真的不错 还有比这更好的吗
No, it's great. It's really great. Doesn't get any better than this.

843
00:54:21,857 --> 00:54:23,620
哦, 真的很好
Oh, but it does.

844
00:54:24,293 --> 00:54:25,817
尝尝这个
Check this out.

845
00:54:31,133 --> 00:54:35,092
哇噻, 你们看那
Wow. Would you look at that.

846
00:54:35,170 --> 00:54:39,664
就像是成千上万亿的直升飞机
It's like billions and billions of helicopters.

847
00:54:39,742 --> 00:54:42,142
瞧,一颗流星 赶快许个愿!
It's a shooting star. Make a wish. Quick!

848
00:54:42,211 --> 00:54:45,374
噢, 一块肥厚多汁的牛排如何?
Ooh! How about a thick, juicy steak?

849
00:54:45,447 --> 00:54:46,971
你知道吗,艾利克斯?
You know what, Alex?

850
00:54:47,049 --> 00:54:51,713
我向你保证如果我明天还活着 我就一定帮你找一块牛排
I promise you I'm going to find you a steak tomorrow if it kills me.

851
00:54:51,787 --> 00:54:53,084
谢谢, 马蒂
Thanks, Marty.

852
00:54:53,155 --> 00:54:56,215
天不早了 我想我得去...
It is getting late. I guess I'm going to...

853
00:54:56,291 --> 00:54:58,725
我也该去睡觉了
I think I'm going to hit the sack too.

854
00:54:58,794 --> 00:55:00,659
祝大伙做个好梦
Sweet dreams, everyone.

855
00:55:30,959 --> 00:55:32,358
艾利克斯.
Alex.

856
00:55:42,337 --> 00:55:44,066
你在干什么?
What are you doing?

857
00:55:44,907 --> 00:55:49,401
27,28,29 30条黑的,只有29条白的
Twenty-seven, 28, 29. Thirty black and only 29 white.

858
00:55:49,478 --> 00:55:52,311
看来你是黑底带着白条纹的了
Looks like you're black with white stripes after all.

859
00:55:52,381 --> 00:55:53,905
难题解决了. 晚安
Dilemma solved. Good night.

860
00:56:04,626 --> 00:56:08,153
你看到了吧, 艾利克斯 先生在梳理同伴的毛发
You see, Maurice, Mr. Alex was grooming his friend.

861
00:56:08,230 --> 00:56:11,666
很显然他是一个温柔而且有很善心的动物
He is clearly a tender, loving thing.

862
00:56:11,734 --> 00:56:14,669
你怎么可以害怕这样好的人哪?
How can you have the heebie-jeebies for Mr. Alex?

863
00:56:14,737 --> 00:56:18,400
看他 多么可爱呀毛茸茸的
Look at him. He's so cute and plushy.

864
00:56:18,474 --> 00:56:20,999
我觉得他不是在梳理那人的毛发
I don't think he was grooming him.

865
00:56:21,076 --> 00:56:23,544
在我看来他是在品尝那人的味道
Look more like he was tasting him to me.

866
00:56:23,612 --> 00:56:26,945
随你怎么说吧,无所谓 我不在乎
Suit yourself, no matter. I don't care.

867
00:56:27,015 --> 00:56:31,179
很快我的计划就要付诸实施了
Soon we will put my excellent plan to action.

868
00:56:31,253 --> 00:56:33,983
我们所要做的就是等待
All we have to do is wait

869
00:56:34,056 --> 00:56:37,719
等他们熟睡之后
until they are deep in their sleep.

870
00:56:43,398 --> 00:56:46,333
到底要等多久呀!
How long is this going to take?!

871
00:57:12,761 --> 00:57:14,194
哎呀,这可真糟糕!
Well, this sucks!

872
00:57:15,364 --> 00:57:18,128
快醒醒,艾利克斯先生
Wake up, Mr. Alex.

873
00:57:19,268 --> 00:57:21,793
快醒醒,艾利克斯先生
Wake up, Mr. Alex.

874
00:57:22,404 --> 00:57:24,201
太阳都照到屁股了
Rise and shining.

875
00:57:24,273 --> 00:57:27,470
醒醒,先生!
Wakey-waking, Mr. Alex!

876
00:57:27,543 --> 00:57:29,010
醒醒,先生!
Wake up! Alex!

877
00:57:29,545 --> 00:57:30,773
你在嘬手指?
You suck your thumb?

878
00:57:33,816 --> 00:57:36,410
我们这是在哪里? 到底发生了什么事?
Where are we? What the heck is going on?

879
00:57:36,485 --> 00:57:38,749
海滩去哪了? 别急
Where's the beach? Take it easy.

880
00:57:38,821 --> 00:57:41,813
-谁造的这个森林? -别这么惊慌,大怪物
- Who built a forest? - Don't be alarmed, giant freaks.

881
00:57:41,890 --> 00:57:43,084
在你们睡觉的时候,
While you were asleep,

882
00:57:43,158 --> 00:57:47,322
我们轻松的把你们带到了这个小小的天堂
we simply took you to our little corner of heaven.

883
00:57:47,396 --> 00:57:49,660
欢迎来到马达加斯加
Welcome to Madagascar.

884
00:57:49,731 --> 00:57:52,291
-马达加谁呀? -什么?
- Mada-who-ah? - What?

885
00:57:52,367 --> 00:57:54,733
不,不是谁呀, 是斯加
No, not whooha. Ascar.

886
00:58:02,377 --> 00:58:04,072
马蒂,这里...
Marty. It's...

887
00:58:04,146 --> 00:58:06,706
就想动物园里墙上的壁画一样
Just like my mural back at the zoo.

888
00:58:06,782 --> 00:58:10,946
哦, 不, 朋友们, 那可全是真的
Oh, no, fella, that is the real deal right there.

889
00:58:11,019 --> 00:58:13,078
瞧那儿, 景色真不错
Look at that, that's not a bad view.

890
00:58:13,155 --> 00:58:17,057
那可是你一直梦寐以求的呀, 现在它就在那里
That's the thing that you were always looking at, but it's actually there.

891
00:58:17,192 --> 00:58:20,593
-那可是真正的... -游览一下整个公园如何?
- That's the real version of... - How about once around the park?

892
00:58:20,762 --> 00:58:24,095
让我们兴奋起来 深呼吸这里的新鲜空气
Let's get our blood pumping, lungs breathing this fresh air.

893
00:58:24,166 --> 00:58:25,565
谁跟我去?!
Who's with me?!

894
00:58:25,634 --> 00:58:28,102
呃,我可不行... 你输了!
Naw. I don't think I could... You're it!

895
00:58:28,170 --> 00:58:29,762
嘿, 想去周围玩玩吗?
Hey! Want to play around?

896
00:58:32,007 --> 00:58:33,201
追上你了!
Got you there!

897
00:58:33,275 --> 00:58:34,640
来这边!
Come here!

898
00:58:35,010 --> 00:58:36,204
你输了
You're it.

899
00:58:36,278 --> 00:58:39,008
嘿, 不比了! 嘿, 你疯了!
Hey, stop that! Hey, you're crazy!

900
00:58:39,615 --> 00:58:42,175
好的, 马蒂, 我不行了
Okay, Marty, I'm it.

901
00:58:42,251 --> 00:58:44,742
我不行了, 受不了了. 你赢了
I'm it. I'm it. You win.

902
00:58:44,820 --> 00:58:47,311
快点, 艾利克斯, 打起精神来
Come on, Alex, get in the groove.

903
00:58:47,389 --> 00:58:49,289
我已经两天没吃饭了
I haven't eaten in two days.

904
00:58:49,358 --> 00:58:52,486
我的血糖太低了 快没劲了
My blood sugar's real low. I just don't have the energy.

905
00:58:52,561 --> 00:58:54,426
我可不觉得那是什么问题
I don't think that's your problem.

906
00:58:54,496 --> 00:58:57,192
首先, 这可不是在草原上奔跑的状态
First of all, that's not how you run in the wild.

907
00:58:57,266 --> 00:58:59,234
我们走. 开足马力准备上路了!
Let's go. Put the rubber to the road!

908
00:58:59,301 --> 00:59:01,292
你就是要把狮子的本色发挥出来
You just have to let out that inner lion.

909
00:59:01,370 --> 00:59:04,806
- 现在, 那头狮子是谁? - 马蒂, 我真的...
- Now, who's the cat? - Marty, I really don't...

910
00:59:04,873 --> 00:59:08,036
你行的, 那是谁 快点! 我们走!
You are, that's who. Come on! Here we go!

911
00:59:08,110 --> 00:59:10,908
就是那样. 咱们再跑的快点! 你狮子
That's it. Let's build up some steam! You the cat.

912
00:59:10,979 --> 00:59:12,571
- 那只狮子是谁? -就是你
- Who's the cat? - You the cat.

913
00:59:12,648 --> 00:59:14,240
那只狮子是谁? -就是你
- Who's the cat? - You the cat.

914
00:59:14,316 --> 00:59:17,911
那只狮子是谁? 就是你 那只狮子是谁? 就是你
Who's the cat? Who's the cat? Who's the cat? Who's the cat?

915
00:59:17,986 --> 00:59:22,116
那只狮子是谁? 就是你 那只狮子是谁? 就是你
Who's the cat? Who's the cat? Who's the cat? Who's the cat?

916
00:59:23,458 --> 00:59:25,255
我是狮子!
I'm the cat!

917
00:59:31,066 --> 00:59:32,533
天那!
Surprise!

918
00:59:40,042 --> 00:59:41,566
你赢了. 你赢了!
You're it. You're it!

919
00:59:41,643 --> 00:59:43,941
追不上狮子, 跑的太快了
Can'tjuke the cat. Cat's too quick.

920
00:59:46,915 --> 00:59:52,251
我感觉好象有一英里长的熏牛肉 在眼前飞舞一直飞上天!
I feel like a mile-high pastrami on rye on the fly from the deli in the sky!

921
00:59:53,255 --> 00:59:56,281
-让我们去撒野吧! -我正想说呢!
- Let's go wild! - Now you're talking!

922
01:00:03,432 --> 01:00:06,128
哥们! 我感觉不一样了
Man! I feel different.

923
01:00:06,201 --> 01:00:09,500
跳啊,跳啊,跳啊 跳啊,跳啊,跳啊!
Noogie, noogie, noogie. Noogie, noogie, noogie!

924
01:00:10,973 --> 01:00:13,134
就像充足了电似的
Kind of charged up or something.

925
01:00:13,208 --> 01:00:16,006
-就像你说的,宝贝,这里... -缺少刺激
- Like you said, baby, it's... - Crackalacking.

926
01:00:16,078 --> 01:00:20,515
- 这样对吗? -哦,对,哦,是的
- Ain't that right, Melman? - Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah.

927
01:00:23,218 --> 01:00:24,776
我在天堂
I'm in heaven.

928
01:00:24,853 --> 01:00:29,790
你看,艾利克斯现在成了我们的朋友 而且马岛B不见了
You see, Maurice, Alex is now our friend and the fossas are nowhere to be seen.

929
01:00:29,858 --> 01:00:32,759
可以说我的计划奏效了
It could be said that my plan is working

930
01:00:32,828 --> 01:00:36,127
以一种非常好的方式
in a very good working kind of way.

931
01:00:36,198 --> 01:00:39,326
艾利克斯,你应该尝尝这个
Alex. You got to try some of this.

932
01:00:40,969 --> 01:00:43,437
我感觉很好 感觉又像个国王了
I feel good. Feel like a king again.

933
01:00:44,272 --> 01:00:45,432
国王?
King?

934
01:00:46,241 --> 01:00:48,038
你应该看看他的架势
You should see his act.

935
01:00:48,110 --> 01:00:51,307
快点,艾利克斯,为什么 不给他露两手你威风的样子呢?
Come on, Alex, why don't you show him some of your act.

936
01:00:51,380 --> 01:00:54,281
哦,不, 我真觉得我... 好吧
Oh. No, I really don't think I could... Okay.

937
01:00:54,349 --> 01:00:57,614
女士们先生们 所有的动物们
Ladies and gentlemen. Primates of all ages.

938
01:00:57,686 --> 01:00:59,813
野生世界自豪地向你们介绍:
The wild proudly presents:

939
01:00:59,888 --> 01:01:01,355
国王
The king.

940
01:01:01,423 --> 01:01:04,221
雄师艾利克斯!
Alex the lion!

941
01:01:05,227 --> 01:01:06,489
大家欢迎
E flat, fellas.

942
01:01:15,937 --> 01:01:18,667
耶! 国王掌管一切!
Yeah! The king is in the house!

943
01:01:18,740 --> 01:01:22,608
看, 如果他是国王,那他的王冠在哪里? 我这里有一个
See, if he is the king, then where is his crown? I've got a crown.

944
01:01:22,677 --> 01:01:25,805
有一个非常漂亮的 就在我头上
Got a very nice one. And it's here on my head.

945
01:01:25,881 --> 01:01:27,849
你看一下, 我戴了没?
Look at it. Have I got it on?

946
01:01:34,122 --> 01:01:36,147
吼一嗓子,伙计,吼一嗓子
Do the roar, man. Do the roar.

947
01:01:41,296 --> 01:01:44,629
哇. 我从来没听过这样的吼叫声
Wow. I've never heard that one before.

948
01:01:44,699 --> 01:01:46,929
好耶! 再疯狂点,哥们!加油!
Yeah! Go wild, man! Come on!

949
01:01:48,470 --> 01:01:49,698
掀起点人浪!
Break out the wave!

950
01:02:16,598 --> 01:02:18,759
打扰一下
Excuse me.

951
01:02:18,834 --> 01:02:21,064
你咬着我屁股了
You're biting my butt.

952
01:02:23,371 --> 01:02:25,839
-不,我没有呀 -你咬了
- No, I'm not. - Yes, you are.

953
01:02:27,742 --> 01:02:29,835
-你干什么呀? -你咬我了!
- What did you do? - You just bit me!

954
01:02:29,911 --> 01:02:32,072
不, 我没有,有吗?
No. I didn't. Did I?

955
01:02:32,147 --> 01:02:33,705
你是咬了
You kind of did.

956
01:02:33,782 --> 01:02:35,909
你到底怎么回事?
What the heck is wrong with you?

957
01:02:37,652 --> 01:02:38,914
你为什么咬我?
Why'd you bite me?

958
01:02:38,987 --> 01:02:41,785
