I'm the one, baby! Come on. Time to robot.

1123
01:16:05,726 --> 01:16:07,887
我是个聪明的国王
I am very clever king.

1124
01:16:08,663 --> 01:16:10,255
我是个超级天才
I am super genius.

1125
01:16:10,331 --> 01:16:12,925
我是机器人国王, 控制猴子的世界
I am robot king of the monkey things.

1126
01:16:13,000 --> 01:16:16,527
-计算机,计算机 -中午吃什么?
- Compute, compute. - So, what's for lunch?

1127
01:16:18,906 --> 01:16:20,840
-闭上眼睛 -为什么非得闭呢?
- Close those eyes. - Why do I have to?

1128
01:16:20,908 --> 01:16:22,375
-照着做 -闭上了
- Do it. - They're closed.

1129
01:16:22,443 --> 01:16:24,308
-再紧点 -是,先生
- Tighter. - Yes, sir.

1130
01:16:24,378 --> 01:16:26,107
-不许偷看 -闭上了
- No peeking. - They're closed.

1131
01:16:26,180 --> 01:16:27,943
瑞可
Rico.

1132
01:16:31,819 --> 01:16:32,877
嗨
Hai.

1133
01:16:34,555 --> 01:16:35,749
把仓门打开
Open that hatch.

1134
01:16:36,691 --> 01:16:39,216
洞里着了火. 现在嚼吧
Fire in the hole. Now chew.

1135
01:16:40,027 --> 01:16:42,621
认真的咀嚼 慢慢享用吧
Chew like you mean it. Savor it.

1136
01:16:43,464 --> 01:16:45,227
-然后? -好的?
- And? - Well?

1137
01:16:45,299 --> 01:16:47,164
相当不错, 对吗?
Pretty good, right?

1138
01:16:47,234 --> 01:16:49,634
总是有B计划的
There's always Plan B.

1139
01:16:51,305 --> 01:16:53,239
这可比牛排好多了
This is better than steak.

1140
01:16:53,307 --> 01:16:55,070
我喜欢.我喜欢!
I love it. I love it!

1141
01:16:55,142 --> 01:16:57,133
小猫喜欢小鱼
The kitty loves the fishy.

1142
01:16:59,914 --> 01:17:02,280
好了, 我提议大家举杯
Well, I propose a toast.

1143
01:17:02,350 --> 01:17:05,285
现在, 也许有时他屁股还会疼...
Now, he may be a pain in the butt at times...

1144
01:17:05,353 --> 01:17:07,480
但是相信我, 我知道
And trust me, I know.

1145
01:17:07,555 --> 01:17:10,251
这只猫毫无疑问地想我证明了
But this cat proved to me without a doubt

1146
01:17:10,324 --> 01:17:12,758
他的胸怀比胃口大
that his heart is bigger than his stomach.

1147
01:17:12,827 --> 01:17:14,624
-敬艾利克斯 -敬艾利克斯
- To Alex. - To Alex.

1148
01:17:21,936 --> 01:17:23,494
够了! 停一下吧!
Enough! Stop it!

1149
01:17:25,306 --> 01:17:28,434
你觉得如何? 我们还要回到纽约去吗?
What do you think? Should we head back to New York?

1150
01:17:28,509 --> 01:17:31,000
我不知道,我是说 这是你的梦想
I don't know. I mean, this is your dream.

1151
01:17:31,078 --> 01:17:33,069
你确定要离开吗?
You sure you want to leave?

1152
01:17:33,147 --> 01:17:35,115
我不在乎身在何处
I don't care where we are.

1153
01:17:35,182 --> 01:17:38,481
只要我们在一起 在哪都行
As long as we're together, it doesn't matter to me.

1154
01:17:38,552 --> 01:17:40,179
好吧,既然这样...
Well, in that case...

1155
01:17:40,254 --> 01:17:43,417
你, 瑞可 我要定300个再走
Yo. Rico. I'll take 300 orders to go.

1156
01:17:43,491 --> 01:17:44,822
嗨
Hai.

1157
01:17:44,892 --> 01:17:48,623
但是在你们走之前 我有个事情要宣布
But before you leave, I have an announcement to make.

1158
01:17:48,696 --> 01:17:51,665
所以请大家安静一下 谢谢
So shut up, everyone, please. Thank you.

1159
01:17:51,732 --> 01:17:56,294
经过一翻深思熟虑
After much deep and profound brain things inside my head,

1160
01:17:56,370 --> 01:17:58,702
我决定要感谢你们
I have decided to thank you

1161
01:17:58,773 --> 01:18:01,503
为我们家带来的和平
for bringing peace to our home.

1162
01:18:01,575 --> 01:18:03,236
还有, 为了让你们不难受
And to make you feel good,

1163
01:18:03,310 --> 01:18:06,143
我要给你们这件可爱的告别礼物
I'm going to give you this lovely parting gift.

1164
01:18:06,213 --> 01:18:09,046
不, 我不能,真的 我不能拿你的王冠
No, I couldn't. Really, I can't take your crown.

1165
01:18:09,116 --> 01:18:11,607
没关系 我还有个更大的
That's okay, I've got a bigger crown.

1166
01:18:11,685 --> 01:18:12,982
上面还有只壁虎
It's got a gecko on it.

1167
01:18:13,054 --> 01:18:16,251
看他发抖的 走, 走!
Look at him shake. Go, Stevie, go!

1168
01:18:17,291 --> 01:18:17,358
-再见,小毛绒桶! -谢谢你们为我们做的一切!
- Bye, little fuzzbuckets! - Thanks for everything!
- Bye, little fuzzbuckets! - Thanks for everything!

1169
01:18:17,358 --> 01:18:20,122
-再见,小毛绒桶! -谢谢你们为我们做的一切!

1170
01:18:20,194 --> 01:18:21,684
-再见 -再见了
- So long! - Bye-bye, now.

1171
01:18:21,762 --> 01:18:23,354
-再来啊 -再见
- Arrivederci. - Bye-bye.

1172
01:18:23,431 --> 01:18:26,093
-再见! -回见,鳄鱼
- Toodle-oo! - See you later, crocodile.

1173
01:18:26,167 --> 01:18:29,261
莫里斯, 我胳膊累了 你帮我挥
Maurice, my arm is tired. Wave it for me.

1174
01:18:30,104 --> 01:18:32,368
快点, 你这淘气的小猴子
Faster, you naughty little monkey.

1175
01:18:32,440 --> 01:18:35,807
等我们回到纽约 就正直寒冬时节
By the time we get back to New York, it'll be the middle of winter.

1176
01:18:35,876 --> 01:18:37,901
所以我就在想,为什么要着急回呢?
So I was just thinking, why rush?

1177
01:18:37,978 --> 01:18:40,913
也许我们可以在回去的路上小停几站
Maybe we could make a few side stops along the way.

1178
01:18:40,981 --> 01:18:43,381
-也许去趟巴黎 -我也这么想的
- Maybe Paris. - You just read my mind.

1179
01:18:43,451 --> 01:18:45,885
-我还想去西班牙 -和公牛赛跑
- I was thinking Spain. - Run with the bulls.

1180
01:18:45,953 --> 01:18:48,717
-斐济如何? -可不可以去趟,加拿大
- What about Fiji? - Canada. Can we?

1181
01:18:48,789 --> 01:18:50,654
药很便宜
Cheap meds.

1182
01:18:50,724 --> 01:18:53,420
我甚至不介意过段时间再来趟这里
I wouldn't even mind coming back here sometime.

1183
01:18:53,494 --> 01:18:55,826
- 我也会的 - 我举双手赞同
- I could do that. - You could say that again.

1184
01:18:55,896 --> 01:18:58,865
-老大... -我一直想去澳大利亚
- Skipper? - I always wanted to go to Australia.

1185
01:18:58,933 --> 01:19:02,528
你说我们该不该告诉他们船没汽油了?
Don't you think we should tell them that the boat's out of gas?

1186
01:19:02,603 --> 01:19:03,729
不要
Nah.

1187
01:19:03,804 --> 01:19:07,706
就保持微笑, 挥手, 孩子们 挥手微笑
Just smile and wave, boys. Smile and wave.

1188
01:19:12,400 --> 01:19:16,900
马达加斯加 -=结束=-
